## CSS (same look as screenshot)

```css
.poh-page{
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 10px;
  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
  color:#1a1a1a;
}

.poh-section{ margin-top: 10px; }
.poh-section-title{
  font-size: 32px;
  font-weight: 650;
  margin: 0 0 18px;
}

.poh-form{ max-width: 900px; }

.poh-row{
  display:flex;
  align-items:flex-start;
  gap: 24px;
  padding: 12px 0;
}

.poh-label{
  width: 330px;
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 14px;
  color:#333;
  margin: 0;
  padding-top: 6px;
}

.poh-field{ flex: 1; }

.poh-select{
  width: 520px;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: 36px;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  border: 1px solid #cfcfcf;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background:#fff;
  font-size: 14px;
}

.poh-radio-group{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap: 10px;
  padding-top: 2px;
}

.poh-radio{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.poh-radio input{ transform: translateY(1px); }

.poh-checklist{
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  gap: 10px;
  padding-top: 2px;
}

.poh-check{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
}
.poh-check input{ transform: translateY(1px); }

@media (max-width: 820px){
  .poh-row{ flex-direction: column; }
  .poh-label{ width: 100%; text-align:left; }
}
```

